---
title: HelloHero: Italian Pork & Potato-Top Pie with Baby Leaves & Parmesan Topping
description: Sometimes only a pie will do. Satisfy that craving for something warm, herby and comforting with this rich, cheesy mash-topped
number. It’s Nonna’s cooking, fused with an explosion of flavour and a dinner that reminds us why at-home cooking is best.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66177face677f43ae029a5f2-6b1e0073.jpeg
